Install MSYS from "https://www.msys2.org/"
Run the installer and run MSYS2 using the commands below
Update the package database. Run the following command inside the MSYS2 terminal> pacman -Syu
Install MinGW-w64 (64-bit)> pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-gcc
For 32-bit> pacman -S mingw-w64-i686-gcc
Install CMake> pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-cmake
For 32-bit> pacman -S mingw-w64-i686-cmake
Add "C:\msys64\mingw64\bin" to Environment path
Verify installtion of gcc and cmake> gcc --version, cmake --version
